plot outline: Ajay is a happy-go-lucky spoil brat. Ajay gets into rivalry with Vikram who is his opponent in college. Ajay falls for Vikram's sister, Nandini, who reciprocates his love. Misunderstandings lead Nandini to hate Ajay. How Ajay wins Nandini and convinces both the families forms the plot of Ajay Passayyadu
